  "notes": "Data taken from the RFEG club page for REAL LA MANGA CLUB (id=542), which lists all rated recorridos for Campo Sur with per-hole Hdcp/Par/Metros and Vc/Vs per tee/gender; cross-checked against the club's official website scorecard, which matches hole-for-hole (pars, stroke indexes, all four tee distances, ratings, slopes). Par 73 (out 37, in 36); stroke index identical for all tees and both genders (RFEG shows one SI allocation). Per-hole distance sums equal published totals exactly for every tee (6499/6127/5739/5139 m). Each tee is rated for both genders, so two entries per tee share identical distances. Minor discrepancy: the club-website extraction showed hole 18 SI as 18, but RFEG lists SI 5 (18 is already hole 2's SI, so RFEG's permutation-valid value is used). RFEG lists designers as Robert Dean Putman and Dave Thomas; course remodeled by Arnold Palmer (2005). The resort's other rated courses (Campo Oeste, Campo Norte) and the par-47 pitch & putt were excluded as out of scope."
